task.summary: EntityRoles changed from bitset to class Props moved out to Base repo
removed conditional template callers via props compile-type checking, replaced with virtual ifaces, it is a little slower but more readable and common
wierd including of client headers changed to better full templating
Added EntityBase, which now contains roles mask, all Entity types must derive from it defered entity destruction (dying flag)

changes for new typedefs removed warnings Mask moved to Base lib flags reworked: - each entity has two sets of flags - double buffer fashion - when flag is "Resolved": -- flag bit is moved from next_flags to curr_flags, and zeroed in curr_flags -- also entity is added to FlaggedSystems, which is new type of system that updates only flagged entities -- its entity list is cleared each frame added simple profiling of systems

each system now contains bitset of contained entities in its EntitiesList added EntityAccessor - helper base class for classes manipulating multiple components' data of entity added Entity::emitEvent() added RolesComposition helper class Systems can now subscribe to and recieve events and flags notifications on their relevant entities SystemFlagged is now SystemScheduled - entities must be scheduled each update cycle SystemAll - loops each relevant entities all the time added systems profiling added SDL2 example inspired by EntityX & compilation with emscripten +some minor changes
